rev.desc.rev.desc: added the ability to remove duplicates from a structured array. If the array type of 'structure' is passed in the code now takes a path that will accomodate the structured array.
By default if no array type is passed in then the code assumes a character array
removed a debugging statement from the start panel $G.test="test"
This application now also removes all the NULL values from the array.
